public class DependencyEval

Evaluates the dependency accuracy of a tree (based on HeadFinder dependency judgments). TODO spence Feb 2010: Trees not only need to implement the HasIndex interface, but also the head finding algorithm must set the index() annotation for each phrasal node according to the head.
